BatchGetAggregateResourceConfig.name: BatchGetAggregateResourceConfig
BatchGetAggregateResourceConfig.description:
Returns the current configuration items for resources that are present in your AWS
                                                Config aggregator

BatchGetResourceConfig.name: BatchGetResourceConfig
BatchGetResourceConfig.description: Returns the current configuration for one or more requested resources

DeleteAggregationAuthorization.name: DeleteAggregationAuthorization
DeleteAggregationAuthorization.description:
Deletes the authorization granted to the specified configuration aggregator account
                                                in a specified region

DeleteConfigRule.name: DeleteConfigRule
DeleteConfigRule.description: Deletes the specified AWS Config rule and all of its evaluation results

DeleteConfigurationAggregator.name: DeleteConfigurationAggregator
DeleteConfigurationAggregator.description:
Deletes the specified configuration aggregator and the aggregated data associated
                                                with the aggregator

DeleteConformancePack.name: DeleteConformancePack
DeleteConformancePack.description:
Deletes the specified conformance pack and all the AWS Config rules and all evaluation
                                                results within that conformance pack.

DeleteEvaluationResults.name: DeleteEvaluationResults
DeleteEvaluationResults.description: Deletes the evaluation results for the specified Config rule

DeleteOrganizationConfigRule.name: DeleteOrganizationConfigRule
DeleteOrganizationConfigRule.description:
Deletes the specified organization config rule and all of its evaluation results from
                                                all member accounts in that organization.

DeleteOrganizationConformancePack.name: DeleteOrganizationConformancePack
DeleteOrganizationConformancePack.description:
Deletes the specified organization conformance pack and all of its evaluation results
                                                from all member accounts in that organization.

DeletePendingAggregationRequest.name: DeletePendingAggregationRequest
DeletePendingAggregationRequest.description:
Deletes pending authorization requests for a specified aggregator account in a specified

DeleteRemediationExceptions.name: DeleteRemediationExceptions
DeleteRemediationExceptions.description:
Deletes one or more remediation exceptions for specific resource keys for a specific
                                                AWS Config Rule.

DeleteResourceConfig.name: DeleteResourceConfig
DeleteResourceConfig.description: Records the configuration state for a custom resource that has been deleted.

DeliverConfigSnapshot.name: DeliverConfigSnapshot

                                                delivery channel

DescribeAggregateComplianceByConfigRules.name: DescribeAggregateComplianceByConfigRules

DescribeAggregationAuthorizations.name: DescribeAggregationAuthorizations
DescribeAggregationAuthorizations.description: Returns a list of authorizations granted to various aggregator accounts and regions

DescribeComplianceByConfigRule.name: DescribeComplianceByConfigRule

DescribeComplianceByResource.name: DescribeComplianceByResource

DescribeConfigurationRecorderStatus.name: DescribeConfigurationRecorderStatus

DescribeConformancePackCompliance.name: DescribeConformancePackCompliance

DescribeOrganizationConformancePackStatu.name: DescribeOrganizationConformancePackStatuses

DescribeOrganizationConformancePacks.name: DescribeOrganizationConformancePacks

DescribePendingAggregationRequests.name: DescribePendingAggregationRequests

DescribeRemediationConfigurations.name: DescribeRemediationConfigurations

DescribeRemediationExceptions.name: DescribeRemediationExceptions
DescribeRemediationExceptions.description: Returns the details of one or more remediation exceptions.

DescribeRemediationExecutionStatus.name: DescribeRemediationExecutionStatus
DescribeRemediationExecutionStatus.description:
Provides a detailed view of a Remediation Execution for a set of resources including
                                                state, timestamps and any error messages for steps that have failed

DescribeRetentionConfigurations.name: DescribeRetentionConfigurations
DescribeRetentionConfigurations.description: Returns the details of one or more retention configurations

GetAggregateConfigRuleComplianceSummary.description:

GetAggregateDiscoveredResourceCounts.name: GetAggregateDiscoveredResourceCounts
GetAggregateDiscoveredResourceCounts.description:
Returns the resource counts across accounts and regions that are present in your AWS

GetAggregateResourceConfig.name: GetAggregateResourceConfig
GetAggregateResourceConfig.description:
Returns configuration item that is aggregated for your specific resource in a specific

GetComplianceDetailsByConfigRule.name: GetComplianceDetailsByConfigRule

Returns the resource types, the number of each resource type, and the total number

Returns detailed status for each member account within an organization for a given

GetOrganizationConformancePackDetailedSt.name: GetOrganizationConformancePackDetailedStatus

ListDiscoveredResources.name: ListDiscoveredResources

Accepts a resource type and returns a list of resource identifiers for the resources

PutConfigurationAggregator.name: PutConfigurationAggregator

Creates and updates the configuration aggregator with the selected source accounts

PutConformancePack.name: PutConformancePack
PutConformancePack.description: Creates or updates a conformance pack.

SelectResourceConfig.name: SelectResourceConfig

Accepts a structured query language (SQL) SELECT command, performs the corresponding

TagResource.name: TagResource
